00:17:33.439 --> 00:17:39.520
And with their powers combined, we're able to generate a reproducible validation report at the

00:17:39.520 --> 00:17:45.040
click of a button or at the build of a package because it lives in the vignettes folder. And

00:17:45.040 --> 00:17:48.800
when you build it, you can tell it to execute your vignettes so you can make sure that you don't

00:17:48.800 --> 00:17:55.119
have an R package that has failed its validation. And we generate this exact same report that we

00:17:55.119 --> 00:18:00.959
had before. But now you know where all this came from. We wrote in these signature pages here.

